                                                                                                                                     NATION BRIEFS
                   
	 Hajipur, Jan. 13 (PTI): An eight-year-old boy who earns a living by selling gutkha at the Hajipur railway station lost his leg today after he was thrown in front of an approaching train by Railway Protection Force jawans. 
     
	The reason: the child had refused to give them the gutkha free. Raju Kumar had to pay the jawans Rs 10 a day to sell his ware on the platform, his mother Manju Devi said in an FIR.
         
	New Delhi (PTI): A man who allegedly called up police 400 times and abused them has been arrested. Private security guard Bhuvan Chandra Pandey, 22, made 276 calls to the emergency police number  100  on Friday night and another 155 calls last night, the police said. All the calls were made from his cellphone, they added.
         
	Lucknow (PTI): Two homeguards allegedly misbehaved with a Spanish girl in the Bara Imambara here when she was visiting the monument with her mother, a professor at IIT Kanpur, superintendent (west) A.K. Rai said. The two have been taken into custody. Narcotics substances were also seized from them, he said.
         
	New Delhi (PTI): The railways have a duty to maintain platforms and will have to compensate a passenger for any injury because of poor upkeep and negligence, the national consumer commission has said.A Mumbai woman has claimed compensation after a footbridge collapse killed her husband and disabled her at Jogeshwari station in 1992.
         
	New Delhi (PTI): Madhur Bhandarkar has turned down an offer to direct a film based on the life of controversial Bangladeshi writer Taslima Nasreen. Actress Tabu was to play the lead role in UTVs yet untitled project. Yes, I refused to work on the project, said Bhandarkar. I must say that for me the project was very interesting. But as you know, the issue is already very controversial. I felt it was not right for me to direct the movie.
                                                            
